import { Box, Button, Dialog, DialogActions, DialogContent, DialogTitle, TextField } from "@material-ui/core"
import { useState } from "react";

const ContactPerson = () => {

    const [ openDialog,setOpenDialog] = useState<boolean>(false);

    const handleClose = () => {setOpenDialog(false);}

    return (
        <Box m={5}>

            <Button variant="outlined" color="primary" onClick={() => setOpenDialog(true)}>
                Add Contact Person
            </Button>

            <Dialog open={openDialog} onClose={handleClose} aria-labelledby="form-dialog-title">
                <DialogTitle id="form-dialog-title">Contact Person</DialogTitle>
                <DialogContent>
                   
                    <TextField variant="outlined" margin="normal" label="Name" type="text" fullWidth />
                    <TextField variant="outlined" margin="normal" label="Email Address" type="email" fullWidth />
                    <TextField variant="outlined" margin="normal" label="Address" type="text" fullWidth />
                    <TextField variant="outlined" margin="normal" label="Phone Number" type="text" fullWidth />
                </DialogContent>
                <DialogActions>
                    <Button onClick={handleClose} color="primary">
                        Save
                    </Button>
                    <Button onClick={handleClose} color="primary">
                        Close
                    </Button>
                </DialogActions>
            </Dialog>
        </Box>
    )
}

export default ContactPerson
